{"data":[{"date":"12:54 19/08","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Sassuolo vs Inter Milan 01h30 ng\u00e0y 20/8 (Serie A 2018/19)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Italia","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/19/nhan-dinh-sassuolo-vs-inter-milan-01h30-ngay-208-serie-a-201819.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Sassuolo vs Inter Milan l\u00fac 01h30 ng\u00e0y 20/8 (V\u00f2ng 1 gi\u1ea3i V\u0110QG Italia Serie A 2018/19): Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 h\u00f4m nay, \u00fd ki\u1ebfn chuy\u00ean gia, d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, ph\u00e2n t\u00edch chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tin t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea b\u00ean l\u1ec1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Sassuolo vs Inter Milan 01h30 ng\u00e0y 208 Serie A 201819 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Sassuolo vs Inter Milan 01h30 ng\u00e0y 208 Serie A 201819 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/19/sassuolo-inter.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Sassuolo vs Inter Milan</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2 style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/nhan-dinh-bong-da-c344-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1</span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span> Sassuolo vs Inter Milan: 1-0<br>\r\n</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></h2>\r\n<div>Th\u1eddi gian Sassuolo m\u1edbi th\u0103ng h\u1ea1ng Serie A, Inter \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 t\u1edbi 2 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e8 b\u1eb9p \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 v\u00f9ng Emilia-Romagna v\u1edbi c\u00f9ng t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 7-0. Nh\u01b0ng k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb sau tr\u1eadn v\u00f9i d\u1eadp 7-0 v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 9/2014, Inter \u0111\u00e3 li\u00ean t\u1ee5c g\u1eb7p h\u1ecda khi \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u Sassuolo. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n6/7 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t gi\u1eefa \u0111\u00f4i b\u00ean \u1edf Serie A, Inter tr\u1eafng tay. \u0110\u1ec9nh \u0111i\u1ec3m l\u00e0 cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ecd s\u1ee9c \u1edf v\u00f2ng \u00e1p ch\u00f3t m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc, khi Sassuolo \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ed1 s\u1ed1ng c\u1ed1 ch\u1ebft \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Inter 2-1 ngay t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Giuseppe Meazza. Sassuolo khi \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn tr\u1ee5 h\u1ea1ng, Inter th\u00ec \u0111ang ch\u1ea1y \u0111ua quy\u1ebft li\u1ec7t gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 ch\u00f3t d\u1ef1 Champions League c\u00f9ng Lazio.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nCh\u00ednh ho\u00e0n c\u1ea3nh tr\u1edb tr\u00eau \u1ea5y, c\u00f9ng m\u00e0n \u0103n m\u1eebng \u0111\u1ea7y ph\u1ea5n kh\u00edch c\u1ee7a th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n v\u00e0 c\u00e1c h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Sassuolo t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Giuseppe Meazza \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn gi\u1edbi Interista c\u0103m gi\u1eadn \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 v\u00f9ng Emilia-Romagna t\u1edbi t\u1eadn x\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ee7y. M\u1ed9t m\u00e0n b\u00e1o th\u00f9 ng\u1ecdt ng\u00e0o l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1c Interista li\u00ean t\u1ee5c nh\u1eafc t\u1edbi t\u1eeb khi bi\u1ebft Nerazzurri s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Mapei \u1edf tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ec3 b\u00e1o th\u00f9, ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 l\u00f2ng quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 gi\u1eadn d\u1eef l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ee7. Inter \u0111\u00fang l\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u t\u00e2n binh ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng trong m\u00f9a H\u00e8, nh\u01b0ng vi\u1ec7c mua h\u1ee5t Luka Modric khi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i qu\u00e2n \u00e1o xanh-\u0111en kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 b\u1ed5 sung ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ea1i tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa. V\u1edbi ca ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a Radja Nainggolan, Inter hi\u1ec7n kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 n\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3ng vai tr\u00f2 \u201cb\u1ed9 n\u00e3o\u201d trong l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i.\u00a0 <br>\r\n<br>\r\nVi\u1ec7c Sassuolo th\u1eafng Inter t\u1edbi 6 l\u1ea7n qua 3 \u0111\u1eddi HLV (Roberto Mancini, Stefano Pioli v\u00e0 Luciano Spalletti) ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i v\u00ec may m\u1eafn, m\u00e0 b\u1edfi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 k\u1ef5 gi\u01a1 nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i qu\u00e2n \u00e1o xanh-\u0111en. D\u00f9 \u0111\u00e3 m\u1ea5t Matteo Politano v\u00e0o tay ch\u00ednh Inter, nh\u01b0ng Sassuolo v\u1eabn c\u00f2n Domenico Berardi, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi b\u1ed5 sung c\u1ef1u binh Kevin-Prince Boateng. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ghana t\u1eebng nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 Inter khi c\u00f2n l\u00e0 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t c\u1ee7a Milan giai \u0111o\u1ea1n 2010-2013.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nSassuolo c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh ch\u00fa c\u1eebu ngoan ngo\u00e3n khi \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 Juve, nh\u01b0ng lu\u00f4n ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t t\u01b0ng b\u1eebng, l\u00e0 kh\u00fac x\u01b0\u01a1ng kh\u00f3 g\u1eb7m cho nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 l\u1edbn c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i nh\u01b0 Napoli, Roma v\u00e0 nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 Inter. K\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 sau khi HLV Eusebio Di Francesco ra \u0111i v\u00e0o m\u00f9a H\u00e8 2017, truy\u1ec1n th\u1ed1ng n\u00e0y v\u1eabn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Sassuolo gi\u1eef v\u1eefng. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nInter \u0111\u00e3 thua Sassuolo 6/7 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t n\u00ean vi\u1ec7c ph\u1ea3i h\u00e0nh qu\u00e2n \u0111\u1ebfn s\u00e2n Mapei kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i tin t\u1ed1t l\u00e0nh cho \u0111\u1ed9i qu\u00e2n \u00e1o xanh-\u0111en. N\u1ebfu th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Spalletti kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t \u0111\u00eam nay, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i th\u00ec c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec \u0111\u00f3 qu\u00e1 g\u00e2y s\u1ed1c!<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTH\u00d4NG TIN<br>\r\nSassuolo: V\u1eafng Peluso, Lemos (ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng).<br>\r\nInter: V\u1eafng Nainggolan (ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng).<br>\r\nTheo ch\u00e2u \u00c1, Sassuolo th\u1eafng 5, thua 2/7 tr\u1eadn ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y; th\u1eafng 4, thua 2/6 tr\u1eadn s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t. <br>\r\nTheo ch\u00e2u \u00c1, Inter th\u1eafng 2, h\u00f2a 1, thua 3/6 tr\u1eadn v\u1eeba qua; th\u1eafng 3, h\u00f2a 1, thua 4/8 tr\u1eadn s\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1eb6C BI\u1ec6T<br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 2 b\u00e0n<br>\r\n5/6 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y c\u1ee7a Inter, 5/7 tr\u1eadn v\u1eeba qua c\u1ee7a Sassuolo \u0111\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 t\u1ed1i \u0111a 2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. 4/5 m\u00f9a g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t, tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Inter c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 t\u1ed1i \u0111a 2 b\u00e0n. Tin cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ecd s\u1ee9c \u0111\u00eam nay c\u0169ng s\u1ebd c\u00f3 k\u1ecbch b\u1ea3n t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo Bongdaplus.vn</div>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5663","checkdouble":"194803"},{"date":"12:58 19/08","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Torino vs Roma 23h00 ng\u00e0y 19/8 (Serie A 2018/19)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Italia","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/19/nhan-dinh-torino-vs-roma-23h00-ngay-198-serie-a-201819.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Torino vs Roma l\u00fac 23h00 ng\u00e0y 19/8 (V\u00f2ng 1 gi\u1ea3i V\u0110QG Italia Serie A 2018/19): Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 h\u00f4m nay, \u00fd ki\u1ebfn chuy\u00ean gia, d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, ph\u00e2n t\u00edch chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tin t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea b\u00ean l\u1ec1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Torino vs Roma 23h00 ng\u00e0y 198 Serie A 201819 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Torino vs Roma 23h00 ng\u00e0y 198 Serie A 201819 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/19/view-roma.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Torino vs Roma</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2 style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/nhan-dinh-bong-da-c344-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1</span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span> </span></span></span></span></span>Torino vs Roma: 1-2<br>\r\n</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></h2>\r\n<div>Sau m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i kh\u00e1 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng v\u1edbi v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 3 \u1edf Serie A v\u00e0 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft Champions League, Roma l\u1ea1i nu\u00f4i tham v\u1ecdng l\u1edbn \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y. Nh\u01b0ng n\u1ebfu mu\u1ed1n ph\u1ebf tru\u1ea5t Juventus trong cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua Scudetto, B\u1ea7y s\u00f3i c\u1ea7n kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ed9ng th\u1eadt t\u1ed1t tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng kh\u00e1c c\u1ee7a th\u00e0nh Turin l\u00e0 Torino.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201c\u1ede Roma, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i lu\u00f4n n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 cu\u1ed9c chi\u1ebfn gi\u00e0nh Scudetto, nh\u01b0ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n. Nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf n\u00ean m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd h\u01a1n, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t Juventus s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t nguy hi\u1ec3m khi c\u00f3 th\u00eam Cristiano Ronaldo. Roma d\u0129 nhi\u00ean c\u0169ng r\u1ea5t m\u1ea1nh, nh\u01b0ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u th\u1eadt t\u1ed1t\u201d. Kevin Strootman \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i v\u1eady tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o cu\u1ed9c chinh ph\u1ee5c \u1edf Serie A 2018/19. V\u00e0 nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 H\u00e0 Lan, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng \u201cngh\u1ecb s\u0129\u201d c\u1ee7a Giallorossi sau 5 n\u0103m g\u1eafn b\u00f3, c\u0169ng ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 l\u1eddi tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 Roma kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 y\u1ebfu \u0111i d\u00f9 m\u1ea5t 2 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t l\u00e0 Alisson v\u00e0 Radja Nainggolan trong m\u00f9a H\u00e8. Ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, 14 b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi m\u00e0 G\u0110TT Monchi mang v\u1ec1 \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap Giallorossi t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh \u1edf t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c tuy\u1ebfn. Trong \u0111\u00f3, s\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Javier Pastore, Steven N\u2019Zonzi hay Robin Olsen s\u1ebd \u0111em l\u1ea1i kinh nghi\u1ec7m cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng. C\u00f2n Justin Kluivert, Ante Coric v\u00e0 Bryan Cristante l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 cho t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai. C\u00f3 th\u1ec3, s\u1ebd ch\u1ec9 2 trong s\u1ed1 c\u00e1c t\u00e2n binh \u1ea5y l\u00e0 Olsen v\u00e0 Pastore \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh \u0111\u00eam nay. Nh\u01b0ng b\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3, Giallorossi v\u1eabn \u0111\u1ee7 m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng t\u1ea1i t\u1ed5 \u1ea5m c\u1ee7a Torino.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00ec qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ee9ng v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda Roma. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 ch\u1ec9 thua 1 trong 16 l\u1ea7n g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t g\u1eb7p Torino \u1edf Serie A (th\u1eafng 11, h\u00f2a 4). Roma c\u0169ng b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 6 tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t (th\u1eafng 4, h\u00f2a 2). C\u1ea3 m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc, Giallorossi ch\u1ec9 thua 1 tr\u1eadn s\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch \u1edf Serie A (th\u1eafng 12, h\u00f2a 6), k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c c\u1ee7a CLB. V\u00e0 \u1edf 3 l\u1ea7n g\u1eb7p nhau \u1edf v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean trong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9, Roma c\u0169ng 2 l\u1ea7n gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng. Ch\u01b0a h\u1ebft, trong khi HLV Eusebio Di Francesco c\u1ee7a Roma c\u00f3 th\u00e0nh t\u00edch \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u kh\u00e1 c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng v\u1edbi Torino (th\u1eafng 5, h\u00f2a 3, thua 5), th\u00ec \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y Walter Mazzarri c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 l\u1ea1i r\u1ea5t s\u1ee3 Giallorossi khi thua 11, h\u00f2a 5 v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 th\u1eafng 6 trong 22 l\u1ea7n ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1ef1u trung, c\u1ea3 qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9 l\u1eabn hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ec1u \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch. V\u00e0 s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng ng\u1ea1c nhi\u00ean n\u1ebfu \u0111\u00eam nay, B\u1ea7y s\u00f3i n\u1ed1i d\u00e0i th\u00e0nh t\u00edch \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Torino. \u0110\u1ec3 ki\u1ebfm 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u1edf Serie A m\u00f9a n\u00e0y, v\u00e0 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh tham v\u1ecdng chinh ph\u1ee5c \u1edf m\u00f9a th\u1ee9 2 g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi HLV Di Francesco, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t m\u00e0n ra m\u1eaft r\u1ea5t \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n61 - L\u1eadt l\u1ea1i qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9, Roma v\u1eabn \u0111ang chi\u1ebfm \u01b0u th\u1ebf v\u1ec1 th\u00e0nh t\u00edch \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u01b0\u1edbc Torino. Trong 146 l\u1ea7n hai \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n nhau \u1edf Serie A, Roma th\u1eafng t\u1edbi 61 tr\u1eadn (t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 th\u1eafng 41,7%), h\u00f2a 40 v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 nh\u1eadn 45 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTH\u00d4NG TIN XUNG QUANH<br>\r\n- Roma kh\u00f4ng thua k\u00e8o ch\u00e2u \u00c1 \u1edf 6/9 l\u1ea7n 2 \u0111\u1ed9i g\u1eb7p nhau tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 (th\u1eafng 4, h\u00f2a 2).<br>\r\n- Roma kh\u00f4ng thua k\u00e8o ch\u00e2u \u00c1 \u1edf 4/6 l\u1ea7n g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch c\u1ee7a Torino (th\u1eafng 2, h\u00f2a 2).<br>\r\n- Roma kh\u00f4ng thua k\u00e8o ch\u00e2u \u00c1 \u1edf 7/10 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y (th\u1eafng 5, h\u00f2a 2), v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng thua k\u00e8o ch\u00e2u \u00c1 \u1edf 5/6 tr\u1eadn s\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t (th\u1eafng 3, h\u00f2a 2).<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1eb6C BI\u1ec6T<br>\r\nT\u00e0i c\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn<br>\r\n5/6 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 gi\u1eefa 2 \u0111\u1ed9i c\u00f3 \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. 7/9 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y c\u1ee7a Torino v\u00e0 4/5 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Roma c\u0169ng n\u1ed5 t\u00e0i c\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y s\u1ebd t\u00e1i hi\u1ec7n \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u00eam nay.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo Bongdaplus.vn</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5662","checkdouble":"194804"},{"date":"13:30 19/08","title":"C\u00e1c chuy\u00ean gia n\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/19/link-xem-truc-tiep-u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-nhat-ban-16h00-ngay-198-asiad-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00e0 Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n v\u00e0o l\u00fac 16h00 chi\u1ec1u nay, c\u00e1c chuy\u00ean gia n\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a ra nh\u1eefng quan \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh v\u1ec1 cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ecd s\u1ee9c n\u00e0y.</h2><div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-nhat-ban-asiad-2018-372-194805.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/19/u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-nhat-ban-asiad-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-nhat-ban-asiad-2018-372-194805.html\">TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n 16h00 ng\u00e0y 19/8 (ASIAD 2018)</span><br>\r\nTr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng video clip k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Nh\u1eadt...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00e0 Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n v\u00e0o l\u00fac 16h00 chi\u1ec1u nay, c\u00e1c chuy\u00ean gia n\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a ra nh\u1eefng quan \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh v\u1ec1 cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ecd s\u1ee9c n\u00e0y.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0o l\u00fac 16h00 chi\u1ec1u nay, \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng t\u1ea1i b\u1ea3ng D g\u1eb7p Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n. Sau hai tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ra qu\u00e2n gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng kh\u00e1 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc hai \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng y\u1ebfu Pakistan v\u00e0 Nepal th\u00ec Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 li\u1ec1u thu\u1ed1c th\u1eed c\u1ef1c m\u1ea1nh \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo xem l\u1ea1i nh\u1eefng h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chuy\u00ean gia n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Chuy\u00ean gia n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/19/live-tuong-thuat-truc-tiep-u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-nhat-ban.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>C\u00e1c chuy\u00ean gia n\u1ed9i \u0111\u01b0a ra nhi\u1ec1u quan \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam g\u1eb7p Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede m\u00e0n so t\u00e0i l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0110\u00f4ng B\u1eafc \u00c1 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n nhi\u1ec1u so v\u1edbi Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00e0 c\u00e1c chuy\u00ean gia b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u0169ng c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng quan \u0111i\u1ec3m ri\u00eang v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00e0 U23 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n, c\u1ef1u HLV Nguy\u1ec5n Th\u00e0nh Vinh tin t\u01b0\u1edfng th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Park Hang Seo s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng l\u00e9p v\u1ebf so v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1ecb c\u1ef1u HLV SLNA cho hay:&nbsp;&ldquo;Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00e0 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n c\u00f3 \u00fd ngh\u0129a ph\u00e2n \u0111\u1ecbnh ng\u00f4i nh\u1ea5t nh\u00ec v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u1ebd c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng toan t\u00ednh \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u1edf v\u00f2ng trong. V\u00ec th\u1ebf, th\u1eadt kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 n\u00f3i U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam hay Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n s\u1ebd ch\u01a1i h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 n\u1ebfu \u0111\u00e1 s\u00f2ng ph\u1eb3ng, U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7. U23 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n th\u1ef1c ch\u1ea5t l\u00e0 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 l\u1ee9a U21 n\u00ean h\u1ecd c\u00f2n thi\u1ebfu kinh nghi\u1ec7m v\u00e0 b\u1ea3n l\u0129nh tr\u1eadn m\u1ea1c. \u0110\u00f3 l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 th\u1ebf m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam khi ch\u00fang ta s\u1edf h\u1eefu 3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u00ean 23 tu\u1ed5i.&nbsp; <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u00e2m th\u1ebf c\u1ee7a U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u1edf \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u00e2u l\u1ee5c c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 r\u1ea5t kh\u00e1c v\u1edbi ng\u00f4i \u00c1 qu\u00e2n VCK U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1. Gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e2y, c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin v\u00e0 nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ec1u, U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam kh\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c g\u00ec ph\u1ea3i e ng\u1ea1i U23 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n&rdquo;.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/goc-nhin-olympic-viet-nam-da-hay-buong-tran-gap-nhat-ban-168-194794.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/15/goc-nhin-olympic-viet-nam-da-hay-buong-tran-gap-nhat-ban.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/goc-nhin-olympic-viet-nam-da-hay-buong-tran-gap-nhat-ban-168-194794.html\">G\u00f3c nh\u00ecn: Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e1 hay bu\u00f4ng tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n?</span><br>\r\nKhi m\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft v\u1edbi Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam, li\u1ec7u h\u1ecd s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u00e1 h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c hay bu\u00f4ng \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i?</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1ec1 ph\u1ea7n m\u00ecnh, chuy\u00ean gia b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u0110o\u00e0n Minh X\u01b0\u01a1ng l\u1ea1i \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 quan \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u00e1 h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c: &ldquo;T\u00f4i cho r\u1eb1ng Vi\u1ec7t Nam n\u00ean \u0111\u00e1 h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c. \u0110\u00e2y v\u1eabn l\u00e0 s\u00e2n ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb. Ch\u00fang ta c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1 \u00edt tr\u1eadn nh\u01b0ng thu ho\u1ea1ch nhi\u1ec1u t\u1eeb l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i hay nh\u1eefng th\u1eed nghi\u1ec7m, c\u00f2n h\u01a1n \u0111\u00e1 th\u00eam m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn m\u00e0 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng thi \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3m \u0111i. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1edf ph\u00e0o khi tr\u00e1nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c nh\u01b0ng ch\u1eafc g\u00ec Malaysia \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 d\u1ec5 ch\u01a1i. V\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 s\u1ed1 m\u1ed9t v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng tr\u1ebb l\u00e0 gi\u1eef \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tinh th\u1ea7n thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 kh\u00e1t khao chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng. Ch\u00fang ta c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1 v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh m\u1ed9t ho\u1eb7c \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh hai v\u1edbi Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n, nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ec1u ph\u1ea3i ch\u01a1i h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c&rdquo;.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/asiad-2018/lich-thi-dau-asiad-2018-ngay-hom-nay-198-cua-doan-ttvn-472-194789.html\">L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u ASIAD 2018 ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 19/8 c\u1ee7a \u0111o\u00e0n TTVN</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/asiad-2018/lich-thi-dau-va-ket-qua-bong-da-nam-asiad-2018-472-193926.html\">L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam Asiad 2018</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n tr\u1ebb \u0110\u1eb7ng Ph\u01b0\u01a1ng Nam l\u1ea1i tin t\u01b0\u1edfng \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u00e1 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1ea1nh.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u1ef1u tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam cho hay: &ldquo;T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng, nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n nh\u01b0 gi\u1ea3i U23. C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u00fang ta s\u1ebd pressing m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n, t\u00f9y th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m. HLV Park Hang Seo trong \u0111\u1ee3t t\u1eadp trung n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 cho \u0111\u1ed9i t\u1eadp nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ed1i \u0111\u00e1 kh\u00e1c nhau. T\u00f4i ngh\u0129, Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd duy tr\u00ec l\u1ed1i \u0111\u00e1 pressing t\u1eeb gi\u1eefa s\u00e2n v\u00e0 tranh ch\u1ea5p quy\u1ebft li\u1ec7t \u1edf khu v\u1ef1c n\u00e0y, ch\u1ee9 kh\u00f4ng l\u00f9i s\u00e2u v\u1ec1 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f4ng&rdquo;.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00e0 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra l\u00fac 16h00 v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Bongda24h.vn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp. Mong b\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ecdc ch\u00fa \u00fd \u0111\u00f3n xem.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhan-dinh-olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-nhat-ban-16h00-ngay-198-khi-3-diem-khong-con-nhieu-y-nghia-168-194784.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/16/nhan-dinh-olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-nhat-ban-16h00-ngay-198-khi-3-diem-khong-con-nhieu-y-nghia.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhan-dinh-olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-nhat-ban-16h00-ngay-198-khi-3-diem-khong-con-nhieu-y-nghia-168-194784.html\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n (16h00 ng\u00e0y 19/8): Khi 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n nhi\u1ec1u \u00fd ngh\u0129a</span><br>\r\nV\u00e0o chi\u1ec1u nay 19/8, c\u1ea3 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n s\u1ebd b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn tranh ng\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng D. V\u00e0 li\u1ec7u r\u1eb1ng HLV Park Hang Seo c\u00f3 ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ea1o c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 \u0111\u00e1...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;&#10;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5661","checkdouble":"194808"},{"date":"15:01 19/08","title":"TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP N\u1eef Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs N\u1eef Th\u00e1i Lan 18h30 ng\u00e0y 19/8 (Asiad 2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/19/nu-viet-nam-vs-nu-thai-lan-asiad-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp N\u1eef Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs N\u1eef Th\u00e1i Lan: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng video clip k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u N\u1eef Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs N\u1eef Th\u00e1i Lan b\u1ea3ng C m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 n\u1eef Asiad 2018 l\u00fac 18h30 t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 19/8.</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">(\u1ea5n Ctrl + F5 \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u1eadn th\u00f4ng tin m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t)<br>\r\n<br>\r\nKh\u00e1c v\u1edbi hai b\u1ea3ng A v\u00e0 B, b\u1ea3ng C c\u1ee7a m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 n\u1eef ASIAD 2018 ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 3 thay v\u00ec 4 \u0111\u1ed9i tranh t\u00e0i. V\u00e0 2 \u0111\u1ed9i d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u s\u1ebd \u0111i ti\u1ebfp.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nL\u00e1 th\u0103m may r\u1ee7i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a \u0110T n\u1eef Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00e0o \u0111\u00fang b\u1ea3ng C c\u00f9ng Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n v\u00e0 Th\u00e1i Lan. B\u1ea3n th\u00e2n HLV Mai \u0110\u1ee9c Chung c\u0169ng th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn, Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u1edf \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p cao h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00e0 Th\u00e1i Lan. M\u1ed9t su\u1ea5t v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft \u1edf b\u1ea3ng C g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 n\u1eb1m trong tay c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n x\u1ee9 hoa anh \u0111\u00e0o. Nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i s\u1ebd ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00e0 Th\u00e1i Lan.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp N\u1eef Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs N\u1eef Th\u00e1i Lan b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 n\u1eef Asiad 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp N\u1eef Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs N\u1eef Th\u00e1i Lan b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 n\u1eef Asiad 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/19/20180816_100127.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">N\u1eef Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs N\u1eef Th\u00e1i Lan</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ea7n n\u00f3i th\u00eam l\u00e0 3 ng\u00e0y tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u di\u1ec5n ra, Th\u00e1i Lan ch\u1ec9 ch\u1ecbu thua Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n 0-2. Th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 l\u00e0 Vi\u1ec7t Nam kh\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i h\u01a1n th\u1ebf, t\u1ee9c l\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 thua v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 t\u1ed1i thi\u1ec3u tr\u01b0\u1edbc Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i b\u1ea3ng C sau \u0111\u00e2y 2 ng\u00e0y, \u0111\u1ec3 ganh \u0111ua v\u1ec1 hi\u1ec7u s\u1ed1 v\u1edbi Th\u00e1i Lan. Ch\u00ednh v\u00ec th\u1ebf, ngay c\u1ea3 m\u1ed9t k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 h\u00f2a tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00e1c c\u00f4 g\u00e1i x\u1ee9 ch\u00f9a V\u00e0ng chi\u1ec1u nay c\u0169ng khi\u1ebfn Vi\u1ec7t Nam kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n trong vi\u1ec7c ki\u1ebfm v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nDo \u0111\u00f3, m\u1ec7nh l\u1ec7nh ph\u1ea3i th\u1eafng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Mai \u0110\u1ee9c Chung \u0111\u01b0a ra cho c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2. \u201cG\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed9i Th\u00e1i Lan \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u00fang t\u00f4i x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh l\u00e0 quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t. N\u1ebfu th\u1eafng, c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng trong c\u1ee7a \u0110T n\u1eef Vi\u1ec7t Nam l\u00e0 99%. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y\u201d, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n l\u00e3o luy\u1ec7n n\u00e0y kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed8I H\u00ccNH D\u1ef0 KI\u1ebeN<br>\r\nVi\u1ec7t Nam: H\u1ea3i Y\u1ebfn; Ch\u01b0\u01a1ng Th\u1ecb Ki\u1ec1u, H\u1ed3ng Nhung, Ph\u1ea1m Th\u1ecb T\u01b0\u01a1i, Th\u00f9y Dung; Tuy\u1ebft Dung, Nguy\u1ec5n Th\u1ecb Li\u1ec5u, Nguy\u1ec5n Th\u1ecb V\u1ea1n, M\u1ef9 Anh; Hu\u1ef3nh Nh\u01b0, H\u1ea3i Y\u1ebfn. <br>\r\nTh\u00e1i Lan: Nattaruja; Warunee, Sunisan, Natthakarn, Kanjanaporn; Kanjana, Rattikan, Orathai, Pikul, Silawan; Taneekarn.</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5660","checkdouble":"194816"},{"date":"16:56 19/08","title":"K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u b\u1ea3ng D Asiad 2018","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/19/10-7412-1534671506_600x0.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chuy\u00ean trang Bongda24h c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt chi ti\u1ebft k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u b\u1ea3ng D m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam Asiad 2018 h\u00f4m nay. Th\u00f4ng tin k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1, ng\u01b0\u1eddi ghi b\u00e0n, di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn ch\u00ednh, tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n 16h00 chi\u1ec1u ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 19/8.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 hi\u1ec7p 1 U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n: 1-0<br>\r\nNg\u01b0\u1eddi ghi b\u00e0n: Quang H\u1ea3i (3')</div>\r\n<hr>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/8/19/Highlight-U23-Viet-Nam-vs-U23-Nhat-Ban-hiep-1.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/link-sopcast/link-xem-truc-tiep-u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-nhat-ban-16h00-ngay-198-asiad-2018-302-194819.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/19/link-xem-truc-tiep-u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-nhat-ban-16h00-ngay-198-asiad-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/link-sopcast/link-xem-truc-tiep-u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-nhat-ban-16h00-ngay-198-asiad-2018-302-194819.html\">Link xem tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n 16h00 ng\u00e0y 19/8 (Asiad 2018)</span><br>\r\nLink xem tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u b\u1ea3ng D m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam Asiad 2018, \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng link c\u00e1c c\u00e1ch xem tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Olympic...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 1/8, vi\u1ec7c th\u1eafng hay thua Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n qu\u00e1 quan tr\u1ecdng v\u1edbi \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u00fd do HLV Park Hang Seo \u0111\u00e3 tung ra m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 v\u1eafng m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a nhi\u1ec1u g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t ch\u1ee7 ch\u1ed1t nh\u01b0 C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng, Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng, Anh \u0110\u1ee9c hay V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi Nh\u1eadt chi\u1ec1u Ch\u1ee7 Nh\u1eadt 19/8.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Asiad 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Asiad 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/19/10-7412-1534671506_600x0.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Quang H\u1ea3i gi\u00fap Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1edbm v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">TUy nhi\u00ean \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng l\u00e0m Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam gi\u1ea3m \u0111i s\u1ef1 nguy hi\u1ec3m. Ngay \u1edf ph\u00fat th\u1ee9 3 c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, t\u1eeb m\u1ed9t pha t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng, c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 HLV Park Hang Seo \u0111\u00e3 g\u00e2y s\u1ee9c \u00e9p l\u00ean h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n, khi\u1ebfn h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd m\u1eafc l\u1ed7i nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng gi\u00fap Quang H\u1ea3i c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 ngay \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng l\u00e0m v\u1ed1n, l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1eb7t n\u1eb7ng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 th\u1eafng thua ngay t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u, c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1 t\u1ef1 tin v\u00e0 tung ra kh\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng nguy hi\u1ec3m v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda c\u1ea7u m\u00f4n \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng cho th\u1ea5y s\u1ef1 s\u1eafc s\u1ea3o trong c\u00e1c pha l\u00ean b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. C\u00e1c pha t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd nhanh b\u00f3ng b\u1ecb h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 Vi\u1ec7t Nam b\u1ebb g\u00e3y. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y khi\u1ebfn hi\u1ec7p 1 tr\u00f4i qua v\u1edbi ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n \u1edf m\u1ee9c trung b\u00ecnh. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u00eam b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u1edf 45 ph\u00fat thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, hai \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e0nh ra s\u00e2n t\u1ea1m ngh\u1ec9 v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 t\u1ea1m th\u1eddi l\u00e0 1-0. N\u1ebfu t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 n\u00e0y gi\u1eef nguy\u00ean t\u1edbi h\u1ebft tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd gi\u00e0nh ng\u00f4i nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng D v\u00e0 s\u1ebd g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed9i h\u1ea1ng 3 \u1edf 1 trong 3 b\u1ea3ng B/E/F t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 1/8 s\u1eafp t\u1edbi.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5659","checkdouble":"194818"},{"date":"16:22 19/08","title":"Clip b\u00e0n th\u1eafng Quang H\u1ea3i m\u1edf \u0111i\u1ec3m cho U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/19/clip-ban-thang-quang-hai-mo-diem-cho-u23-viet-nam.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Video clip b\u00e0n th\u1eafng Quang H\u1ea3i ghi b\u00e0n m\u1edf t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 cho \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 3 b\u1ea3ng D Asiad 2018.</h2><h2>&nbsp;Video clip b\u00e0n th\u1eafng Quang H\u1ea3i ghi b\u00e0n m\u1edf t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 cho \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 3 b\u1ea3ng D Asiad 2018.</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Video clip b\u00e0n th\u1eafng Quang H\u1ea3i m\u1edf \u0111i\u1ec3m cho U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Video clip b\u00e0n th\u1eafng Quang H\u1ea3i m\u1edf \u0111i\u1ec3m cho U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/19/video-quang-hai-mo-diem-cho-u23-viet-nam.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Video Quang H\u1ea3i m\u1edf \u0111i\u1ec3m cho U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nT\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng sai l\u1ea7m c\u1ee7a h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng th\u1ee7 U23 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u1edf ngay ph\u00fat th\u1ee9 3, Quang H\u1ea3i d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng cho ri\u00eang m\u00ecnh. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng th\u1ee9 2 c\u1ee7a Quang H\u1ea3i trong gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u0103m nay<br>\r\n<h3>Clip Quang H\u1ea3i ghi b\u00e0n m\u1edf t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 cho Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</h3>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/8/19/U23-Viet-Nam-vs-U23-Nhat-Ban-03.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-nhat-ban-asiad-2018-372-194805.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/19/u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-nhat-ban-asiad-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-nhat-ban-asiad-2018-372-194805.html\">TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP hi\u1ec7p 2 U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n 16h00 ng\u00e0y 19/8 (ASIAD 2018)</