n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Video Clip highlight k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 hi\u1ec7p 1 U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam 1-0 U23 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Video Clip highlight k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 hi\u1ec7p 1 U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam 1-0 U23 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/19/clip-highlight-hiep-1-u23-viet-nam-1-0-u23-nhat-ban.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nNgay ph\u00fat th\u1ee9 3 c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng sai l\u1ea7m c\u1ee7a h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 U23 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n, \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho V\u0103n To\u00e0n \u0111o\u1ea1t b\u00f3ng \u1edf g\u1ea7n khu v\u1ef1c c\u1ea5m \u0111\u1ecba \u0111\u1ed9i b\u1ea1n v\u00e0 mau ch\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ea9y b\u00f3ng cho Quang H\u1ea3i. R\u1ea5t b\u00ecnh t\u0129nh, ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a CLB H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i \u0111\u1eb7t l\u00f2ng tung l\u01b0\u1edbi Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n. Nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat ti\u1ebfp theo tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u di\u1ec5n ra \u1edf th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng, m\u1eb7c d\u00f9 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ea1o ra nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 th\u00eam b\u00e0n th\u1eafng n\u00e0o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ghi. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n<h3>Video U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam 1-0 U23 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n hi\u1ec7p 1 b\u1ea3ng D Asiad 2018</h3>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/8/19/Highlight-U23-Viet-Nam-vs-U23-Nhat-Ban-hiep-1.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-nhat-ban-asiad-2018-372-194805.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/19/u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-nhat-ban-asiad-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-nhat-ban-asiad-2018-372-194805.html\">TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP hi\u1ec7p 2 U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n 16h00 ng\u00e0y 19/8 (ASIAD 2018)</span><br>\r\nTr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp hi\u1ec7p 2 U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng video clip k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Nh\u1eadt...</div>\r\n</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5657","checkdouble":"194823"},{"date":"12:13 19/08","title":"Mourinho ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 \u0111ang tr\u1eebng ph\u1ea1t m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 MU","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/11/20/mourinho-tiet-lo-dang-trung-phat-mot-cau-thu-mu.JPG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Theo HLV ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha th\u00ec \u0111\u00f3 ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 trung v\u1ec7 Victor Lindelof. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3 c\u00e2u chuy\u1ec7n \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o?</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Victor Lindelof gia nh\u1eadp Manchester United t\u1eeb Benfica v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 30 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i. Tuy nhi\u00ean, n\u0103m \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u1edf Old Trafford c\u1ee7a trung v\u1ec7 tr\u1ebb ng\u01b0\u1eddi Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n kh\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i l\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u01b0 k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng, \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9 anh c\u0169ng ch\u1eb3ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o cho m\u00ecnh m\u1ed9t ch\u1ed7 \u0111\u1ee9ng v\u1eefng ch\u1eafc trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Qu\u1ef7 \u0110\u1ecf.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">M\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y hy v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd kh\u00e1c, nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 sau khi Lindelof m\u1edbi tr\u1ea3i qua m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 World Cup 2018 t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng. \u0110\u00f3 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00e0 HLV Jose Mourinho h\u1ebft m\u1ef1c tin t\u01b0\u1edfng \u1edf c\u1eadu h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 24 tu\u1ed5i, m\u1eb7c d\u00f9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u1ec9 b\u1ea5t \u0111\u1eafc d\u0129 khi \u00f4ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00eam trung v\u1ec7 \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Mourinho n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 trung v\u1ec7 Lindelof c\u1ee7a MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Mourinho n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 trung v\u1ec7 Lindelof c\u1ee7a MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/11/20/tan-binh-nha-201819-hoi-muon-victor-lindelof.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Mourinho n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 trung v\u1ec7 Lindelof c\u1ee7a MU</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/nhan-dinh-brighton-vs-man-utd-22h00-ngay-198-cau-tra-loi-tren-san-co-172-194787.html\" target=\"_blank\">Brighton vs MU \u1edf v\u00f2ng 2 Premier League 2018/19</span>, \u00f4ng c\u00f2n ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 m\u00ecnh \u0111ang tr\u1eebng ph\u1ea1t anh khi b\u1ed1 tr\u00ed s\u1eafp x\u1ebfp thi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00e1i v\u1edbi v\u1ecb tr\u00ed s\u1edf tr\u01b0\u1eddng. Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u c\u1ee5 th\u1ec3 c\u1ee7a nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha: <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i c\u00f3 t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 5 trung v\u1ec7 v\u00e0 m\u1ed7i ng\u01b0\u1eddi trong s\u1ed1 h\u1ecd \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng ph\u1ea9m ch\u1ea5t ri\u00eang c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Th\u1ebf n\u00ean ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sao cho ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p nh\u1ea5t v\u1edbi t\u00ednh ch\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, th\u00e0nh ra c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng ai c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o th\u1eddi gian thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean h\u1ebft.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cT\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean, Victor l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi tr\u1ebb nh\u1ea5t n\u00ean c\u00f3 \u0111\u00f4i ch\u00fat b\u1ea5t l\u1ee3i, nh\u01b0ng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u0169ng c\u00f2n nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n v\u00e0 ho\u00e0n thi\u1ec7n b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n h\u01a1n c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i. \u0110\u00f4i khi, t\u00f4i bu\u1ed9c l\u00f2ng ph\u1ea3i \u2018tr\u1eebng ph\u1ea1t\u2019 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y khi b\u1ed1 tr\u00ed ch\u01a1i \u1edf l\u1ec7ch tr\u00e1i ch\u1ee9 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed l\u1ec7ch ph\u1ea3i s\u1edf tr\u01b0\u1eddng.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cT\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng Victor s\u1ebd c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i Premier League t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i, \u00edt nh\u1ea5t nh\u01b0 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eebng th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u1edf World Cup v\u00e0 c\u1ea3 Champions League, t\u1eeb Lisbon \u0111\u1ebfn Moscow. C\u00f3 v\u1ebb nh\u01b0 Victor ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u00e0 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng h\u01a1n cho c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf, nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n tin t\u01b0\u1edfng v\u00e0o th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng to\u00e0n di\u1ec7n \u1edf c\u1eadu \u1ea5y.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/du-am-mu-20-leicester-172-194221.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/11/du-am-mu-20-leicester.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/du-am-mu-20-leicester-172-194221.html\">Man Utd m\u1edf m\u00e0n su\u00f4n s\u1ebb: Kh\u00f4ng mua \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trung v\u1ec7? Kh\u00f4ng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1!</span><br>\r\nPaul Pogba t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng r\u1ef1c r\u1ee1, Luke Shaw h\u1ed3i sinh m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd, nh\u01b0ng ch\u00ednh c\u1eb7p b\u00e0i tr\u00f9ng h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 Eric Bailly v\u00e0 Victor Lindelof \u1edf tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng MU 2-1 Leicester...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nguoi-bang-victor-lindelof-mot-dang-cap-moi-cho-mu-172-162477.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/6/15/nguoi-bang-victor-lindelof-mot-dang-cap-moi-va-khac-biet-o-old-trafford.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nguoi-bang-victor-lindelof-mot-dang-cap-moi-cho-mu-172-162477.html\">\u201cNg\u01b0\u1eddi b\u0103ng\u201d Victor Lindelof: M\u1ed9t \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p m\u1edbi v\u00e0 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t \u1edf Old Trafford</span><br>\r\nV\u1ecfn v\u1eb9n 18 th\u00e1ng, trung v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t \u0111i\u1ec3m khi\u00eam t\u1ed1n t\u1eeb m\u1ed9t \u201cma m\u1edbi\u201d tr\u00ean b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb Benfica tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u00f3n h\u00e0ng n\u00f3ng tr\u00ean to\u00e0n Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u. V\u1edbi...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5656","checkdouble":"194801"},{"date":"14:59 19/08","title":"\"Pogba v\u00e0 Mourinho c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh h\u01a1n\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/11/pogba-va-mourinho-can-phai-truong-thanh-hon.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Paul Ince cho r\u1eb1ng Mourinho v\u00e0 Pogba c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh h\u01a1n v\u00e0 t\u1eadp trung v\u00e0o kh\u00eda c\u1ea1nh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 thay v\u00ec ch\u00fa \u00fd nhi\u1ec1u v\u00e0o c\u00e1c v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Hai nh\u00e2n v\u1eadt t\u1ea7m c\u1ee1 \u1edf s\u00e2n Old Trafford l\u00e0 Mourinho v\u00e0 Pogba li\u00ean t\u1ee5c xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n tr\u00ean c\u00e1c m\u1eb7t b\u00e1o g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y v\u00ec tin \u0111\u1ed3n c\u00f3 m\u00e2u thu\u1eabn v\u1edbi nhau. Mourinho c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng ch\u1ed1ng tr\u1ea3 l\u1ea1i nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n n\u00e0y v\u00e0 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u00f4ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 vui m\u1eebng h\u01a1n v\u1edbi c\u1eadu h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u01b0ng ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 c\u00f3 v\u1ebb c\u0169ng kh\u00e1 nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng khi Pogba kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u1eb1ng anh s\u1ebd gi\u1ea5u k\u00edn m\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n v\u00ec kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n b\u1ecb ph\u1ea1t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Paul Ince Pogba v\u00e0 Mourinho c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh h\u01a1n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Paul Ince Pogba v\u00e0 Mourinho c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh h\u01a1n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/11/pogba-va-mourinho-can-phai-truong-thanh-hon.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Paul Ince cho r\u1eb1ng Pogba v\u00e0 Mourinho c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh h\u01a1n</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Paul Ince cho r\u1eb1ng Mourinho v\u00e0 Pogba n\u00ean g\u1ea1t b\u1ecf nh\u1eefng m\u00e2u thu\u1eabn v\u00e0 b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u c\u00f9ng nh\u00ecn v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t h\u01b0\u1edbng. Chia s\u1ebb tr\u00ean k\u00eanh BBC v\u1ec1 m\u00e2u thu\u1eabn trong n\u1ed9i b\u1ed9 MU, \u00f4ng cho bi\u1ebft:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cTr\u01b0\u1edbc h\u1ebft, t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 Pogba l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u00e0i n\u0103ng. Ch\u00fang ta \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ea5y t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i. Nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1edbi nhau.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cPogba \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i, gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup v\u00e0 thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng. Mourinho c\u0169ng trao b\u0103ng \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng cho Pogba. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 cho th\u1ea5y \u00f4ng \u1ea5y t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng c\u1eadu h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh ra sao.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cPogba \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n thi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1edbc Leicester v\u00e0 ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt. Nh\u01b0ng sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, Pogba l\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0a ra nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi b\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn ng\u1edb ng\u1ea9n v\u00e0 l\u1ea1i kh\u01a1i d\u1eady tr\u00ed t\u00f2 m\u00f2 c\u1ee7a c\u00e1nh ph\u00f3ng vi\u00ean.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cC\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c duy nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0 ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng n\u00f3i chuy\u1ec7n v\u1edbi t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3. Tranh c\u00e3i n\u00e0y c\u00f3 l\u1ebd s\u1ebd c\u00f2n k\u00e9o d\u00e0i \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m nay.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201c\u0110i\u1ec1u m\u00e0 ch\u00fang ta n\u00ean n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 Man United l\u00e0 h\u1ecd s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfn xa t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2u \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y ch\u1ee9 kh\u00f4ng Mourinho hay Pogba. H\u00e3y \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u1eefng tranh c\u00e3i l\u00f9i v\u1ec1 qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9 v\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh h\u01a1n\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Man United:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nhan-dinh-brighton-vs-man-utd-22h00-ngay-198-cau-tra-loi-tren-san-co-172-194787.html\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Brighton vs Man Utd (22h00 ng\u00e0y 19/8): C\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ecf</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mu-nhan-mot-loat-tin-vui-truoc-tran-gap-brighton-172-194765.html\">M.U nh\u1eadn m\u1ed9t lo\u1ea1t tin vui tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Brighton</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5655","checkdouble":"194812"},{"date":"15:12 19/08","title":"Mourinho th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn MU kh\u00f3 c\u00e1n \u0111\u00edch trong top 4 m\u00f9a n\u00e0y","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/11/mourinho-thua-nhan-mu-kho-can-dich-trong-top-4-mua-nay.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Jose Mourinho cho r\u1eb1ng Man United kh\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u1ec1 \u0111\u00edch trong top 4 \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m nay.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Man United \u0111\u00e3 v\u1ec1 \u0111\u00edch \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u00c1 qu\u00e2n t\u1ea1i Premier League m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc. Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t danh hi\u1ec7u n\u00e0o k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb khi Sir Alex Ferguson gi\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec7 v\u00e0o n\u0103m 2013.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, HLV Jose Mourinho cho r\u1eb1ng c\u00e1c C\u0110V Man United s\u1ebd c\u00f2n ph\u1ea3i ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i th\u00eam n\u1eefa n\u1ebfu mu\u1ed1n ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u0111\u0103ng quang v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Premier League. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed, chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 c\u00f2n kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf s\u1ebd l\u00e0m n\u00ean \u0111i\u1ec1u k\u1ef3 di\u1ec7u n\u1ebfu c\u00e1n \u0111\u00edch trong top 4 m\u00f9a n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Mourinho th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn MU kh\u00f3 c\u00e1n \u0111\u00edch trong top 4 m\u00f9a n\u00e0y h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Mourinho th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn MU kh\u00f3 c\u00e1n \u0111\u00edch trong top 4 m\u00f9a n\u00e0y h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/11/mourinho-thua-nhan-mu-kho-can-dich-trong-top-4-mua-nay.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>HLV Mourinho bi quan v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng MU l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o top 4 Premier League m\u00f9a n\u00e0y</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng nh\u01b0ng m\u1ed9t c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n \u0111ang ch\u1edd ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ph\u00eda tr\u01b0\u1edbc. C\u00e1n \u0111\u00edch \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 2 l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3. V\u00e0 \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u00f9a b\u00f3ng m\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i n\u00e0o c\u0169ng s\u1ebd g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n trong cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua top 4\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1ec1 th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng, Mourinho cho r\u1eb1ng Tottenham, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed Premier League kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t t\u00e2n binh n\u00e0o \u1edf phi\u00ean ch\u1ee3 h\u00e8, l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng nh\u1ea5t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cLiverpool \u0111ang c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng gi\u00e0nh danh hi\u1ec7u v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi. Chelsea c\u0169ng c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng. Man City c\u0169ng v\u1eady. Tottenham c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 qu\u00e1 t\u1ed1t b\u1eb1ng vi\u1ec7c gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t m\u00e0 b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cH\u1ecd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chi ti\u00eau 200 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng nh\u01b0ng n\u1ebfu h\u1ecd m\u1ea5t Kane hay Eriksen th\u00ec m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n. V\u00ec v\u1eady, vi\u1ec7c gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t trong \u0111\u1ed9i c\u0169ng l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng. Arsenal c\u0169ng s\u1ebd c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u d\u00f9 h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 thua c\u1ea3 2 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean. T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 \u0111\u00e2y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nXem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Man United:<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/pochettino-se-khong-tu-choi-neu-duoc-moi-dan-dat-mu-172-194725.html\">Pochettino s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i n\u1ebfu \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1eddi d\u1eabn d\u1eaft MU</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nguoi-cu-mu-khang-dinh-sanchez-khong-phai-bom-xit-172-194719.html\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u0169 MU kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Sanchez kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i bom x\u1ecbt</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nXu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5654","checkdouble":"194817"},{"date":"15:30 19/08","title":"TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP Man City vs Huddersfield 19h30 ng\u00e0y 19/8 (Premier League 2018/19)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/18/man-city-vs-huddersfield-ngoai-hang-anh-1982018.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp Man City vs Huddersfield: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng video clip k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Manchester City vs Huddersfield v\u00f2ng 2 gi\u1ea3i Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh Premier League NHA 2018/19 l\u00fac 19h30 t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 19/8.</h2><h2>Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp Man City vs Huddersfield: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng video clip k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Manchester City vs Huddersfield v\u00f2ng 2 gi\u1ea3i Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh Premier League NHA 2018/19 l\u00fac 19h30 t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 19/8.</h2></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5653","checkdouble":"194821"},{"date":"10:15 19/08","title":"G\u00f3c nh\u00ecn: Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e1 hay bu\u00f4ng tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/15/goc-nhin-olympic-viet-nam-da-hay-buong-tran-gap-nhat-ban.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Khi m\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft v\u1edbi Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam, li\u1ec7u h\u1ecd s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u00e1 h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c hay bu\u00f4ng \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i?\r\n\r\n\r\n</h2><br>\r\n<h2>B\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh thay \u0111\u1ed5i</h2>\r\n<h2><o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam g\u1eb7p Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft c\u1ee7a b\u1ea3ng D, b\u1edfi l\u00fac n\u00e0y hai \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111ang b\u1eb1ng nhau \u1edf m\u1ecdi ch\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 tr\u00ean BXH. C\u00f3 c\u00f9ng 6 \u0111i\u1ec3m, ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 5 b\u00e0n v\u00e0 ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi m\u1ed9t b\u00e0n n\u00e0o, Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00e0 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u0111ang khi\u1ebfn ng\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng D v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e2n \u0111\u00edch th\u1ef1c.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i, n\u1ebfu hai \u0111\u1ed9i ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c h\u00f2a nhau trong 90 ph\u00fat thi \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c th\u00ec theo lu\u1eadt, c\u1ea3 hai s\u1ebd b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o \u0111\u00e1 lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u 11m \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm ra \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u1ebd gi\u00e0nh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i l\u00fac n\u00e0y, v\u1ecb tr\u00ed d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n qu\u00e1 quan tr\u1ecdng v\u1edbi Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam sau khi H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd \u0111\u1ec3 thua Malaysia. Trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p x\u1ebfp nh\u00ec b\u1ea3ng D, ch\u00fang ta s\u1ebd g\u1eb7p Malaysia, \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn gi\u1eef ng\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng E. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Khi m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n nguy c\u01a1 ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Park Hang Seo ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng toan t\u00ednh \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1eef \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t cho tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf v\u00f2ng knock-out s\u1eafp t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"G\u00f3c nh\u00ecn Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e1 hay bu\u00f4ng tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"G\u00f3c nh\u00ecn Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e1 hay bu\u00f4ng tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/16/Goc-nhin-Olympic-Viet-Nam-da-hay-buong-tran-gap-Nhat-Ban-hinh-anh.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>B\u1ea3ng x\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng b\u1ea3ng D ASIAD tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Nh\u1ea5t hay nh\u00ec b\u1ea3ng m\u1edbi quan tr\u1ecdng?<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 ph\u00e2n t\u00edch, n\u1ebfu Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng D, theo c\u00e1ch ph\u00e2n chia c\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a gi\u1ea3i, ch\u00fang ta s\u1ebd g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed9i th\u1ee9 3 \u1edf b\u1ea3ng B (c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 Th\u00e1i Lan, Qatar), ho\u1eb7c \u0111\u1ed9i th\u1ee9 3 b\u1ea3ng E (Bahrain, Kyrgyzstan, H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c) ho\u1eb7c b\u1ea3ng F (Iran, Saudi Arabia hay Tri\u1ec1u Ti\u00ean).<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c g\u1eb7p to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, v\u1ecb tr\u00ed d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng D ch\u01b0a h\u1eb3n \u0111\u00e3 mang l\u1ea1i l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf cho Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam. Ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i n\u1ebfu ch\u1ec9 v\u1ec1 nh\u00ec, ch\u00fang ta s\u1ebd g\u1eb7p Malaysia v\u00e0 khi \u0111\u00f3 c\u1eeda th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo l\u00e0 l\u1edbn h\u01a1n, d\u00f9 th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf Olympic Malaysia kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng t\u1ea7m th\u01b0\u1eddng khi v\u1eeba c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng g\u00e2y s\u1ed1c tr\u01b0\u1edbc H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i trong khu v\u1ef1c \u0110N\u00c1, b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam ch\u01b0a khi n\u00e0o e ng\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi Malaysia. V\u00e0 khi m\u00e0 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng g\u1eb7p nh\u1eefng s\u1ee9c \u00e9p, h\u1ecd ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ee7 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a HLV Ong Kim Swee t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 1/8 s\u1eafp t\u1edbi.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>Ch\u1edd toan t\u00ednh c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y Park<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi nh\u1eefng ph\u00e2n t\u00edch tr\u00ean, r\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 x\u00e1o tr\u1ed9n l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eefng s\u1ebd gi\u00fap HLV Park Hang Seo c\u1ea5t gi\u1eef \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u1ea5t khi b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng 1/8, m\u00e0 n\u00f3 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 d\u1ecbp thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c ki\u1ec3m nghi\u1ec7m n\u0103ng l\u1ef1c nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb, \u00edt c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u00e0o s\u00e2n thi \u0111\u1ea5u.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7, r\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 Ph\u1ea1m Xu\u00e2n M\u1ea1nh s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh ngay t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u thay cho V\u0103n Thanh b\u00ean h\u00e0nh lang c\u00e1nh ph\u1ea3i. Khi \u0111\u00f3 V\u0103n Thanh s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i cho tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"G\u00f3c nh\u00ecn Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e1 hay bu\u00f4ng tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"G\u00f3c nh\u00ecn Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e1 hay bu\u00f4ng tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/15/Goc-nhin-Olympic-Viet-Nam-da-hay-buong-tran-gap-Nhat-Ban-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb \u1edf tr\u1eadn Vi\u1ec7t Nam g\u1eb7p Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd ra s\u00e2n \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm s\u1ef1 \u0103n \u00fd c\u00f9ng H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng. Song c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 anh s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ngh\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u01b0\u1eddng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng hay \u0110\u1ee9c Huy. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">S\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n khi \u0110\u1ee9c Chinh, V\u0103n To\u00e0n v\u00e0o s\u00e2n \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ebf ch\u1ed7 cho Anh \u0110\u1ee9c, Quang H\u1ea3i. Anh \u0110\u1ee9c, Quang H\u1ea3i l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh \u1edf c\u1ea3 hai tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam n\u00ean r\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 h\u1ecd s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i \u0111\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u quan tr\u1ecdng h\u01a1n \u1edf v\u00f2ng trong.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u01a1n h\u1ebft vi\u1ec7c c\u1ea5t \u0111i nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t s\u1ebd gi\u00fap HLV Park Hang Seo gi\u1ea3m thi\u1ec3u r\u1ee7i ro c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo. Khi m\u00e0 Anh \u0110\u1ee9c, Quang H\u1ea3i, V\u0103n Thanh hay Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng,\u2026 \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean c\u00f3 t\u1ea7m \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn tr\u00ean tuy\u1ec3n th\u00ec s\u1ebd l\u00e0 b\u1ea5t l\u1ee3i l\u1edbn cho Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam n\u1ebfu h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c thi \u0111\u1ea5u.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Park Hang Seo\" title=\"Park Hang Seo\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/16/hlv-park-hang-seo-noi-gi-truoc-tran-gap-olympic-nhat-ban.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103n HLV\u00a0Park Hang Seo s\u1ebd tung \u0111\u1ed9i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb g\u1eb7p Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n 4 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u01b0a \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n t\u1ea1i ASIAD l\u00e0 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n V\u0103n Ho\u00e0ng, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 \u0110\u00ecnh L\u1ee3i, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o V\u0103n To\u00e0n. C\u1ea3 4 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n t\u1ed1t v\u00e0 th\u1eeba khao kh\u00e1t kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n n\u1ebfu c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i thi \u0111\u1ea5u. V\u00e0 s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 l\u00fd do g\u00ec m\u00e0 th\u1ea7y Park s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 \u1edf m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f4ng th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 quan tr\u1ecdng s\u1eafp t\u1edbi.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 c\u1ee7a Bongda24h.vn, v\u1edbi t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd bu\u00f4ng tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n. H\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018 v\u1eabn c\u00f2n r\u1ea5t d\u00e0i v\u00e0 th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Park Hang Seo c\u1ea7n c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng toan t\u00ednh h\u1ee3p l\u00fd nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111i t\u1edbi tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a gi\u1ea3i.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhan-dinh-olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-nhat-ban-16h00-ngay-198-khi-3-diem-khong-con-nhieu-y-nghia-168-194784.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/16/nhan-dinh-olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-nhat-ban-16h00-ngay-198-khi-3-diem-khong-con-nhieu-y-nghia.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhan-dinh-olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-nhat-ban-16h00-ngay-198-khi-3-diem-khong-con-nhieu-y-nghia-168-194784.html\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n (16h00 ng\u00e0y 19/8): Khi 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n nhi\u1ec1u \u00fd ngh\u0129a</span><br>\r\nV\u00e0o chi\u1ec1u nay 19/8, c\u1ea3 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n s\u1ebd b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn tranh ng\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng D. V\u00e0 li\u1ec7u r\u1eb1ng HLV Park Hang Seo c\u00f3 ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ea1o c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 \u0111\u00e1...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-mai-duc-chung-dt-viet-nam-se-danh-bai-thai-lan-168-194746.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/13/hlv-mai-duc-chung-dt-viet-nam-se-danh-bai-thai-lan.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-mai-duc-chung-dt-viet-nam-se-danh-bai-thai-lan-168-194746.html\">HLV Mai \u0110\u1ee9c Chung: \u201c\u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Th\u00e1i Lan\u201d</span><br>\r\nChia s\u1ebb tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n t\u1ea1i ASIAD 18 di\u1ec5n ra l\u00fac 18h30 ng\u00e0y 19/8 t\u1edbi, HLV Mai \u0110\u1ee9c Chung \u0111\u00e3 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Th\u00e1i Lan \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/bao-thai-chi-ra-guong-mat-duoc-ky-vong-nhat-cua-olympic-viet-nam-o-asiad-168-194745.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/18/bao-thai-chi-ra-guong-mat-duoc-ky-vong-nhat-cua-olympic-viet-nam-o-asiad.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/bao-thai-chi-ra-guong-mat-duoc-ky-vong-nhat-cua-olympic-viet-nam-o-asiad-168-194745.html\">B\u00e1o Th\u00e1i ch\u1ec9 ra g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u1edf ASIAD</span><br>\r\nT\u1edd b\u00e1o th\u1ec3 thao h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Th\u00e1i Lan, SiamSport m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a ra b\u1ea3n danh s\u00e1ch 9 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e1ng xem nh\u1ea5t ASIAD 2018, trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/thua-soc-malaysia-han-quoc-van-co-kha-nang-gap-olympic-viet-nam-168-194711.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/1/11/thua-soc-malaysia-han-quoc-van-co-kha-nang-gap-olympic-viet-nam.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/thua-soc-malaysia-han-quoc-van-co-kha-nang-gap-olympic-viet-nam-168-194711.html\">Thua s\u1ed1c Malaysia, H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c v\u1eabn c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng g\u1eb7p Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span><br>\r\nTheo c\u00e1ch chia b\u1ea3ng v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u lo\u1ea1i tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp, \u0110T Olympic H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c v\u1eabn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd ch\u1ea1m m\u1eb7t Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam n\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi x\u1ea3y ra.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;\nline-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5652","checkdouble":"194794"},{"date":"11:01 19/08","title":"Sarri gi\u1ea3i th\u00edch v\u00ec sao Chelsea b\u1ecb l\u1ed9i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng trong hi\u1ec7p m\u1ed9t","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/19/sarri-giai-thich-vi-sao-chelsea-bi-loi-nguoc-dong-trong-hiep-mot.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>T\u00e2n HLV ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u00dd qua \u0111\u00e2y c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 ch\u0103m ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n m\u00ecnh h\u01a1n n\u1eefa \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u00e1nh l\u1eb7p l\u1ea1i nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i hi\u1ec7p m\u1ed9t \u1edf tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Arsenal v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean ba \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u1ecdn v\u1eb9n v\u1eabn n\u1eb1m l\u1ea1i Stamford Bridge nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00e1ng l\u1ebd ra Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng v\u00e0 th\u1ea3nh th\u01a1i h\u01a1n nhi\u1ec1u, kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ebfn ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng Marcos Alonso t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng \u0111\u00fang l\u00fac v\u00e0 gi\u1ea3i c\u1ee9u \u1edf th\u1eddi gian cu\u1ed1i tr\u1eadn.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Sarri ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u tr\u1eadn Chelsea vs Arsenal chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Sarri ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u tr\u1eadn Chelsea vs Arsenal chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/19/sarri-giai-thich-vi-sao-chelsea-bi-loi-nguoc-dong-trong-hiep-mot.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Sarri ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u tr\u1eadn Chelsea vs Arsenal derby London</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">L\u1ee3i th\u1ebf d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ebfn hai b\u00e0n ch\u00f3ng v\u00e1nh tan th\u00e0nh m\u00e2y kh\u00f3i ch\u1ec9 trong v\u00f2ng b\u1ed1n ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i hi\u1ec7p m\u1ed9t khi l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t Mkhitaryan v\u00e0 Iwobi tr\u1eebng ph\u1ea1t nh\u1eefng sai l\u1ea7m n\u01a1i h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 nh\u01b0 m\u01a1 ng\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0. Maurizio Sarri vui m\u1eebng v\u1edbi k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng nh\u01b0ng ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn c\u0169ng kh\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u c\u1ee7a t\u00e2n HLV ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u00dd sau tr\u1eadn derby London k\u1ecbch t\u00ednh v\u00e0 ngh\u1eb9t th\u1edf: \u201cTh\u1eadt s\u1ef1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi, v\u1edbi ba \u0111i\u1ec3m kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n nh\u01b0ng ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng cho n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i. Nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00fang v\u1eady, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i n\u00ean b\u1ea3o to\u00e0n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng ngay t\u1eeb trong hi\u1ec7p m\u1ed9t n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 15 ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng ch\u01a1i kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t \u0111\u00f3.\"<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cT\u00f4i ngh\u0129 c\u1ef1 ly \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb k\u00e9o gi\u00e3n ra qu\u00e1 xa v\u00e0 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e1nh m\u1ea5t kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch h\u1ee3p l\u00fd \u0111\u1ec3 k\u1ebft n\u1ed1i v\u1edbi nhau. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 15 ph\u00fat m\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u00e1i b\u00f3ng c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 ch\u01a1i pressing \u0111\u00fang l\u00fac \u0111\u00fang ch\u1ed7, ch\u00ednh th\u1ebf m\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00f3n nh\u1eadn 4-5 l\u1ea7n s\u00f3ng gi\u00f3 chao \u0111\u1ea3o t\u1eeb Arsenal.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">D\u00f9 sao th\u00ec Chelsea v\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7y b\u1ea3n l\u0129nh v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Arsenal v\u00e0 t\u1ea1m th\u1eddi d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng x\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng Premier League 2018/19 sau hai tr\u1eadn to\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0 s\u00e1u \u0111i\u1ec3m tuy\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ed1i. V\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo \u0111\u00e2y, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Sarri s\u1ebd h\u00e0nh qu\u00e2n \u0111\u1ebfn St. James\u2019 Park l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch c\u1ee7a t\u00e2n binh m\u1edbi th\u0103ng h\u1ea1ng Newcastle.</p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Video tr\u1eadn Chelsea 3-2 Arsenal:</h2>\r\n<table class=\"embedMedia\" id=\"embedMedia_279447\" style=\"width:100%;\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\r\n    <tbody>\r